_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/16a667bbacce0dddcce11bd1b355d9c7.webp?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/0f821f515e5385e83950e390321a2913.poster.avif?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/0f821f515e5385e83950e390321a2913.webm?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/0f821f515e5385e83950e390321a2913.mp4?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Mike. Carefree, but sharp. Devoted to his girlfriend, Jenny. He has an office job and a childlike sense of fun mixed with adult confidence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/2f37cfbc66cf2e7163bf772d08c5ae1b.webp?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/148099e9283e0a1e885780f181fba6a4.poster.avif?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=580 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/148099e9283e0a1e885780f181fba6a4.webm?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/148099e9283e0a1e885780f181fba6a4.mp4?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jenny</strong> is your long-term girlfriend. A caring but controlling woman who likes to set the rules in your relationship. Her expectations rise. The intimacy fades. Routine takes over. What do you do next?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/3697d5ce56b9340a4bfa2eda78c15a75.webp?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=60 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/00efad827bb7acba137bc5035e7bdb8d.poster.avif?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=580 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/00efad827bb7acba137bc5035e7bdb8d.webm?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/00efad827bb7acba137bc5035e7bdb8d.mp4?t=1775859114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maria</strong> is Jenny’s cousin. She moves in with you to escape the turmoil at home. She is 18, super shy, and incredibly attractive. Curiosity, temptation, and voyeurism creep in, challenging your loyalty. You both know it's wrong, but it's up to you how far you choose to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3859850/extras/cf1c60792eef3c948615027dd2c74f11.webp?t=1775859114\" width=1170 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shar